message.body: I hope you are feeling better and find out what's wrong. Your mutha told me (this is George).
Hey Georgie! Thanks, I spent the day in the emergency eye specialists, so far they can't find anything wrong w me, but I'm still dizzy..so weird
Hey George, I meant to write back saturday but I was on the subway and it didn't send and I forgot to resend. I'm ok, I have ear rocks, which make me crazy diZzy.
Thanks for checking in, I hope you are well! Take care
Thank you. I hope your ear rocks turn to sand and pour out of your ears, comfortably ;)
I did a weird head exercise which I think lodged them into my brainz...but I think that was the point? I'm seeing a doctor tomorrow, they will tell me what's up
Oh, wow. I have no idea. Lodging anything into the brain sounds pretty painful. Godspeed.
It just made me dizzy. Thanks Georgie!
Awe. Let me know how things go.
Hey Georgie! Will you be around at Xmas?
We should go out Xmas night! Le shamrock!
I'll be there for xmas dinner, at 1 pm. The full spread. There's a large party around the corner from it on lemon st after. Can't wait to see yah!
I should talk iris into going to the shamrock for Xmas dinner! What time is the party?
Not sure exactly prob like 7 or 8. She would love it. I am going to my 'rents at like 9am and not eating, so i can be back and eat there.
Hahaha..I'm a total omnivore now, so I would love to hit a spread : )
